Class KeyedOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • emissary.output.roller.journal.KeyedOutput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable, ByteChannel, Channel, ReadableByteChannel, SeekableByteChannel, WritableByteChannel
    public class KeyedOutput
extends OutputStream
implements SeekableByteChannel
    Lightweight wrapper holding reference to a pooled object and the pool, which returns the channel to the pool on close.
